      ****************************************************************
      *
      *                  VIAP0056-TRATA-ERRO-BANKA
      ****************************************************************
      *
       VIAP0056-TRATA-ERRO-BANKA.
      *
            MOVE VIAW0056-MSGQ              TO BRCL1020-PGMQ.
            MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAW0056-COD-ERR.
      *
            CALL 'BR1020' USING BRCL1020-PGMQ
                                BRCL1020-WRMG-H
                                BRCL1020-WNOCORN






            PERFORM VARYING VIAW0056-INDEX FROM 1 BY 1
              UNTIL (VIAW0056-INDEX > 10)
                 OR BRCL1020-WRMG(VIAW0056-INDEX) EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE BRCL1020-WRMG(VIAW0056-INDEX) TO VIAW0056-MSG-TOT
      * AUTORIZAﾇﾃO INVﾁLIDA
               IF VIAW0056-MSG = 'GBM0198'
                  MOVE 'VIAP0056-WRMG'
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  MOVE BRCL1020-WRMG(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                     THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
                  MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-ORAUTR TO VIAW0056-COD-ERR
               END-IF
      * NﾃO EXISTEM MOVIMENTOS PARA ANULAR NO DIA
               IF VIAW0056-MSG = 'GBM7536'
                  MOVE 'VIAP0056-WRMG'
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  MOVE BRCL1020-WRMG(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                     THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
                  MOVE PSCK0001-ANUL-DAT-ERR TO VIAW0056-COD-ERR
               END-IF
      * UTILIZADOR SEM AUTORIZAﾇﾃO
               IF VIAW0056-MSG = 'GBM1232'
               OR VIAW0056-MSG = 'GBM0252'
                  MOVE 'VIAP0056-WRMG'
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  MOVE BRCL1020-WRMG(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                     THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
                  MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-USER-AUTR TO VIAW0056-COD-ERR
               END-IF
      * EXCEDE PLAFOND DO UTILIZADOR
               IF VIAW0056-MSG = 'GBM0201'
                  MOVE 'VIAP0056-WRMG'
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  MOVE BRCL1020-WRMG(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                     THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
                  MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-PLAFOND   TO VIAW0056-COD-ERR
               END-IF
      * ESTORNO Sﾓ PODE SER FEITO PELO BALCﾃO OU UTILIZADOR
      * DO MOVIMENTO
               IF VIAW0056-MSG = 'GBM0266'
                  MOVE 'VIAP0056-WRMG'
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  MOVE BRCL1020-WRMG(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                     THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
                  MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-ESTORNO   TO VIAW0056-COD-ERR
               END-IF
      * AUTORIZAﾇﾃO NﾃO ﾉ VﾁLIDA PARA A DATA
               IF VIAW0056-MSG = 'GBM5177'
                  MOVE 'VIAP0056-WRMG'
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  MOVE BRCL1020-WRMG(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                     THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
                  MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-DTAUTR    TO VIAW0056-COD-ERR
               END-IF
      * CONTA CCC VENCIDA. MOVIMENTO NﾃO EFECTUADO
               IF VIAW0056-MSG = 'GBM3568'
                  MOVE 'VIAP0056-WRMG'
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  MOVE BRCL1020-WRMG(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(VIAW0056-INDEX)
                  PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                     THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
                  MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-CCC-VENC  TO VIAW0056-COD-ERR
               END-IF
            END-PERFORM.
      *
       VIAP0056-TRATA-ERRO-BANKA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
